# Income.International Dealings Foreign Tax Offset Amount

## identifier
de8974

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, for the duration of the relevant period, of a credit available to a taxpayer who received foreign income that is taxable in Australia and for which they paid (or are taken to have paid) foreign tax. This amount includes credits for foreign source capital gains.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Income.InternationalDealings.ForeignTaxOffset.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=duration
